          "usage_instructions": "Get keyword suggestions from search engine autocomplete. QUERY is required (positional). Use --source/-s to select engines (google, youtube, bing, amazon, ddg -- can repeat for multiple). Use --filter/-f to only show suggestions containing specific text. Use --recurse/-r with --depth/-d to recursively expand suggestions (default depth: 1, limit: 5 per level). Use --limit/-l (default: 100), --table/-t.",
